short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A specialized calculator to help with Combinatorics calculations

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a simple combinatorics calculator that computes three types of calculations that are very common in combinatorics.

I made this extension after constantly looking up calculators online to check my work as I did homework. After going to the same site over and over I decided that I needed a better solution.
